!script {{

 --/| Script Name : Character New Ability Creation
 --/| Version     : 2.0
 --/| Requires SC : ScriptCards
 --/| Author      : Farsidegallery
 --/|  
 --/| Script creates abilities on selected character. Script allows user to select if new character or updating existing character. New character is hard-coded to desired base abilities and ends immeadiately after execution. 
 --/| If updating existing character, choose from general, racial, class, or spell categories. Further prompts will prompt user for desired class if class is selected. Next prompt for exact desired ability/spell and if it is 
 --/| a token action. Final prompt is if to add another ability. Outputs are whispered to gm at the end.
 --/| 
 --/| An issue was found when using the LibSN_BUILD_DROPDOWN_FROM_ARRAY from the snlib provided by Kurt. An interaction between the LibSN_BUILD_DROPDOWN_FROM_ARRAY function and the -i function resulted in an extra close bracket.
 --/| This broke the call to the ability on the macro mule specified. A modified version of the LibSN_BUILD_DROPDOWN_FROM_ARRAY function is built into this script.
 --/|
 --/| Planned update to this is when 5E-Action-Menu pulls abilities from mules correctly on all settings, abilities will be copied into reduced number of mules and script will be updated accordingly.
 --/|

  --/| ____________________ Begin Global User Variables -Update the variables below to your game settings. ___________________________________
    
  --/|Enter character IDs for mules in use.
  
  --&MacroMule|General_Macro_Mule
  --&SpellMule|Spell_Mule
  --&RacialMule|Race_Ability_Mule
  --&BarbarianMule|Barbarian_Mule
  
  --/| ____________________ End Global User Variables ___________________________________________________________________________________________

  --#sourceToken|@{selected|token_id}
  --#whisper|gm
  
  --&obrac|{
  --&cbrac|}
  --&perc|%
  
  -->ChooseFunction|
  
  --:ChooseFunction|
   --+Choose Function: |[rbutton]New Token::NewCharacter;[*S:t-id][/rbutton][rbutton]Update::Update;[*S:t-id][/rbutton]
   --X|
  
  --:NewCharacter| 
   --!ob:AbilID1:@{selected|character_id}:AFK:y|%[&obrac][&MacroMule]|AFK[&cbrac]
   --!ob:AbilID2:@{selected|character_id}:DealDamage:n|%[&obrac][&MacroMule]|DealDamage[&cbrac]
   --!ob:AbilID3:@{selected|character_id}:Gather-Information:y|%[&obrac][&MacroMule]|Gather-Information[&cbrac]
   --!ob:AbilID4:@{selected|character_id}:Health-Check:y|%[&obrac][&MacroMule]|Health-Check[&cbrac]
   --!ob:AbilID5:@{selected|character_id}:Long-Rest:y|%[&obrac][&MacroMule]|Long-Rest[&cbrac]
   --!ob:AbilID7:@{selected|character_id}:pingMe:n|%[&obrac][&MacroMule]|pingMe[&cbrac]
   --!ob:AbilID8:@{selected|character_id}:Remove-Aid:n|%[&obrac][&MacroMule]|Remove-Aid[&cbrac]
   --!ob:AbilID9:@{selected|character_id}:Short-Rest:y|%[&obrac][&MacroMule]|Short-Rest[&cbrac]
   --!ob:AbilID10:@{selected|character_id}:5E-Action-Menu:y|%[&obrac][&MacroMule]|5E-Action-Menu[&cbrac]
   --!ob:AbilID10:@{selected|character_id}:Shopping:y|%[&obrac][&MacroMule]|Shopping[&cbrac]
   --!a:@{selected|character_id}|!SmartAOE_ignore:1
   -->OutputNew|
  
  --:OutputNew|
   --%LoopCounter|1;10;1
    --&AbilName|[*O:[&AbilID[&LoopCounter]]:ability:name]
    --+Ability|[&AbilName] added.
    --%|
   --X|
  
  --:EndScript|
   --X|  
}}